    {
        "url": "/quotes/jason_schreier_864352",
        "quote": "Unraveling the threads of a good game story is like solving a well-crafted puzzle. After a lengthy, sometimes difficult journey, the pieces click into place, and you're rewarded with the satisfying payoff of a job well done.",
