    {
        "url": "/quotes/jason_schreier_864332",
        "quote": "Sure, when you think 'World of Warcraft,' you might picture the nerdier set - those who may have sacrificed hygiene and sleep to reach one more experience level. But the truth is that 'WoW' is populated with players of all sorts of backgrounds, from rural housewives to NFL punters.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Jason Schreier",
            "url": "/quotes/jason_schreier_864332"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Reach",
