                "name": "Housewives",
                "url": "/topics/housewives"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/jason_schreier_864347",
        "quote": "Kickstarter can get customers invested, both literally and figuratively, in a game before it is released. With nothing but an idea, a bit of video and a few screenshots, a developer can start building a loyal fan base.",
