                "name": "Weeks",
                "url": "/topics/weeks"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/jason_schreier_864331",
        "quote": "Between 'The Godfather,' 'The Sopranos,' 'Goodfellas,' and the countless other mob stories that have been both critically and commercially acclaimed over the years, it's not hard to see why a game like 'Mafia Wars' works.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Jason Schreier",
            "url": "/quotes/jason_schreier_864331"
        },
