                "name": "Receive",
                "url": "/topics/receive"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/jason_schreier_864318",
        "quote": "To avoid long-term deleterious effects, game developers must commit to stop facilitating a culture in which crunch is the norm. The occasional long night or weekend at the office can be useful and even exhilarating, but as a constant, it is damaging.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Jason Schreier",
            "url": "/quotes/jason_schreier_864318"
        },
        "topics": [
